WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:01.800
If you lose

00:00:01.866 --> 00:00:04.266
Our engagement will be broken off.

00:00:04.266 --> 00:00:06.600
How are you?

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:09.433
This lady speaks very well.

00:00:09.666 --> 00:00:11.500
I promise you won't be scared.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:12.666
I'm afraid you lose.

00:00:12.966 --> 00:00:14.300
I believe you.

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:16.266
Both have such elegance.

00:00:16.266 --> 00:00:18.466
How about a word?

00:00:18.466 --> 00:00:21.300
Okay, Shen Hyun, you handy little guy.

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:24.566
Waiting for you to marry into the Trieu family will definitely make your life worse than death.

00:00:24.566 --> 00:00:26.200
The two started walking.

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:29.733
Miss Shen, you are betting on your engagement.

00:00:29.733 --> 00:00:31.366
Not a bit too impulsive.

00:00:31.366 --> 00:00:32.966
Thank you seven ladies for your concern.

00:00:32.966 --> 00:00:33.766
But...

00:00:34.333 --> 00:00:35.833
I trust A Huc.

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:38.333
Zhang Xudong, I want to see.

00:00:38.333 --> 00:00:40.900
Are you as good as the rumors say?